plot: Two strangers ask Mark for help with a mysterious villain. Elsewhere in the galaxy, Nolan grapples with his identity and Allen finds a surprising new ally.

Mark goes to see Cecil, then has a date with Eve and takes a trip to the future where he meets an old friend overwhelmed by the burdens of his responsibilities and wants Mark to help him. Allen, Nolan, and Battle Beast make an escape from the Viltrumite prison ship.—Gislef
